{"id":17094,"date":"2019-04-30T16:18:19","date_gmt":"2019-04-30T09:18:19","guid":{"rendered":"\/?p=17094"},"modified":"2019-06-20T22:38:58","modified_gmt":"2019-06-20T15:38:58","slug":"website-la-gi-va-gia-tri-cua-no","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"\/wordpress\/website-la-gi-va-gia-tri-cua-no","title":{"rendered":"Website l\u00e0 g\u00ec? S\u1ee1 h\u1eefu m\u1ed9t website \u0111\u00e1ng gi\u00e1 nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0o?"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p class=\"highlight\"><em>M\u1ed7i ng\u00e0y tr\u00ean th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi c\u00f3 h\u01a1n 140.000 website m\u1edbi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kh\u1edfi t\u1ea1o v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 quan ng\u1ea1i l\u00e0n s\u00f3ng ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c m\u1ea1ng x\u00e3 h\u1ed9i, <\/em><strong><em>v\u1eady webiste l\u00e0 g\u00ec<\/em><\/strong><em>?<\/em><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>D\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5y r\u1eb1ng m\u1ea1ng x\u00e3 h\u1ed9i nh\u01b0 Facebook \u0111ang ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n th\u1ea7n t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ebfn n\u1ed7i kh\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u doanh nghi\u1ec7p v\u00e0 c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n kh\u00f4ng quan t\u00e2m c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t website ri\u00eang v\u00e0 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng m\u1ea1ng x\u00e3 h\u1ed9i nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 thay th\u1ebf cho website. B\u1edfi v\u00ec m\u1ea1ng x\u00e3 h\u1ed9i mi\u1ec5n ph\u00ed v\u00e0 d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u00e1c.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Ch\u1ec9 v\u1edbi Facebook Fanpage v\u00e0 Facebook Group b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd fan hay kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Website \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e0m g\u00ec? Qu\u00e1 ph\u1ee9c t\u1ea1p v\u00e0 t\u1ed1n k\u00e9m?<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>V\u1eady b\u1ea1n h\u00e3y t\u00ecm hi\u1ec3u m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 l\u00fd do sau \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ea5y r\u1eb1ng c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t website cho doanh nghi\u1ec7p m\u00ecnh l\u00e0 \u0111\u00e1ng gi\u00e1.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Website l\u00e0 g\u00ec?<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1024\" height=\"518\" src=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/Suki-Website-1024x518.png\" alt=\"Website l\u00e0 g\u00ec\" class=\"wp-image-17137\" srcset=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/Suki-Website-1024x518.png 1024w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/Suki-Website-218x110.png 218w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/Suki-Website-300x152.png 300w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/Suki-Website-700x354.png 700w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/Suki-Website-768x389.png 768w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/Suki-Website.png 1680w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><figcaption>Website c\u1ee7a Suki Theme<\/figcaption><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p>Website l\u00e0 t\u1ed5 h\u1ee3p nh\u1eefng trang web li\u00ean k\u1ebft v\u1edbi nhau d\u1ef1a v\u00e0o t\u00ean mi\u1ec1n c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n. Page module trong WordPress ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 n\u01a1i b\u1ea1n t\u1ea1o t\u1eebng trang web, t\u1eadp h\u1ee3p nh\u1eefng trang web n\u00e0y l\u1ea1i b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd t\u1ea1o \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t website.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Th\u00f4ng th\u01b0\u1eddng khi b\u1ea1n mu\u1ed1n t\u1ea1o blog v\u1edbi WordPress th\u00ec b\u1ea1n c\u0169ng \u0111ang t\u1ea1o website. Blog l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n c\u1ee7a website nh\u01b0ng t\u1eadp trung v\u00e0o xu\u1ea5t b\u1ea3n n\u1ed9i dung th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean. Blog Module l\u00e0 n\u01a1i b\u1ea1n s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1ea5t.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Khi b\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ecbnh h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1ea1o website v\u1edbi WordPress ngh\u0129a l\u00e0 b\u1ea1n mu\u1ed1n t\u1ea1o c\u00e1c trang v\u1edbi n\u1ed9i dung \u00edt c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i. M\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 trang nh\u01b0 Sale Page, Home Page, Check Out Page, Product Page,&#8230; H\u00e3y xem m\u1ed9t website th\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1ea1i \u0111i\u1ec7n t\u1eed l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t v\u00ed d\u1ee5. Website th\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1ea1i \u0111i\u1ec7n t\u1eed ch\u1ee9a r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u landing page, trang s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m, trang thanh to\u00e1n, h\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn giao h\u00e0ng, s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n khuy\u1ebfn m\u00e3i,&#8230;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"Tham kh\u1ea3o website WPAstra \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf v\u1edbi r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u trang v\u00e0 blog \u0111\u1ec3 SEO organic. (opens in a new tab)\" href=\"https:\/\/wpastra.com\/?bsf=2056\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Tham kh\u1ea3o website WPAstra \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf v\u1edbi r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u trang v\u00e0 blog \u0111\u1ec3 SEO organic.<\/strong><\/a><\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1024\" height=\"483\" src=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/Blog-cua-Astra-1024x483.png\" alt=\"Blog Cua Astra\" class=\"wp-image-17142\" srcset=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/Blog-cua-Astra-1024x483.png 1024w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/Blog-cua-Astra-218x103.png 218w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/Blog-cua-Astra-300x142.png 300w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/Blog-cua-Astra-700x330.png 700w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/Blog-cua-Astra-768x362.png 768w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/Blog-cua-Astra.png 1280w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><figcaption>Blog c\u1ee7a WPAstra<\/figcaption><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2>1. Website l\u00e0 gi\u1ea5y Ch\u1ee9ng nh\u1eadn l\u00f2ng tin<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>B\u1ea1n h\u00e3y ch\u00fa \u00fd r\u1eb1ng t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c M\u1ea1ng X\u00e3 H\u1ed9i nh\u01b0 Facebook, LinkedIn, Twitter \u0111\u1ec1u khuy\u1ebfn kh\u00edch v\u00e0 \u01b0u ti\u00ean tr\u01b0ng b\u00e0y website c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n ngay d\u01b0\u1edbi t\u00ean ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00f9ng, b\u1edfi v\u00ec \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 ch\u1ee9ng nh\u1eadn cho th\u00f4ng tin ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00f9ng \u0111\u00e1ng tin c\u1eady.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>N\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eebng review tr\u00ean c\u00e1c trang web l\u1edbn nh\u01b0 <a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"Capterra (opens in a new tab)\" href=\"https:\/\/www.capterra.com\/general-review\/?utm_campaign=ref_au-17293162\" target=\"_blank\">Capterra<\/a> hay <a href=\"https:\/\/www.g2.com\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"G2Crowd (opens in a new tab)\">G2Crowd<\/a>, ngo\u00e0i t\u00e0i kho\u1ea3n LinkedIn \u0111\u1ed9i ng\u0169 ph\u00ea duy\u1ec7t s\u1ebd ki\u1ec3m tra website li\u00ean k\u1ebft \u0111\u1ec3 ph\u00ea duy\u1ec7t review c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>N\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 website li\u00ean k\u1ebft th\u00ec h\u1ea7u nh\u01b0 b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd b\u1ecb t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u0103ng review c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 ph\u1ea7n th\u01b0\u1edfng t\u1eeb h\u1ecd.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1024\" height=\"496\" src=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/Capterra-Review-1024x496.png\" alt=\"Capterra Review\" class=\"wp-image-17201\" srcset=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/Capterra-Review-1024x496.png 1024w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/Capterra-Review-218x106.png 218w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/Capterra-Review-300x145.png 300w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/Capterra-Review-700x339.png 700w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/Capterra-Review-768x372.png 768w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/Capterra-Review.png 1635w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><figcaption>Capterra Review s\u1ebd xem x\u00e9t Proflie LinkedIn v\u00e0 ki\u1ec3m tra website c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n<\/figcaption><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p>Khi b\u1ea1n s\u1edf h\u1eefu website th\u00ec m\u1eb7c \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u1ea1n \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi kinh doanh online. Nh\u1eefng th\u00f4ng tin b\u1ea1n cung c\u1ea5p s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e1ng tin c\u1eady h\u01a1n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3, website c\u0169ng l\u00e0 c\u01a1 s\u1edf \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00e1c c\u00f4ng ty ph\u00ea duy\u1ec7t t\u00e0i kho\u1ea3n affliate c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n. Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 m\u1ea1ng affiliate c\u00f2n \u0111\u00f2i h\u1ecfi website ph\u1ea3i b\u1eb1ng ti\u1ebfng Anh. Kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 website, b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 xin link affiliate.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Website ng\u00e0y nay \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t gi\u1ea5y ch\u1ee9ng nh\u1eadn b\u1ea1n l\u00e0 nh\u00e0 kinh doanh online, l\u00e0 ti\u00eau chu\u1ea9n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean ti\u1ebfn quy\u1ebft cho b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 s\u1ef1 ph\u00ea duy\u1ec7t n\u00e0o tr\u00ean internet.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2>2. Chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ed5i t\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ed9ng 24\/7<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1024\" height=\"622\" src=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/suki-theme-demo-1024x622.png\" alt=\"Suki demo\" class=\"wp-image-17028\" srcset=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/suki-theme-demo-1024x622.png 1024w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/suki-theme-demo-218x132.png 218w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/suki-theme-demo-300x182.png 300w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/suki-theme-demo-700x425.png 700w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/suki-theme-demo-768x467.png 768w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/suki-theme-demo.png 1358w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><figcaption>Click mua h\u00e0ng t\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ed9ng<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>\u01afu \u0111i\u1ec3m tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi c\u1ee7a website l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ed5i t\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ed9ng. B\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o m\u1ed9t trang web v\u00e0 sau \u0111\u00f3 thu h\u00fat traffic v\u00e0 chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ed5i t\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ed9ng th\u00e0nh doanh s\u1ed1 b\u00e1n h\u00e0ng.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>\u0110\u1ed1i v\u1edbi c\u00e1c m\u1ea1ng x\u00e3 h\u1ed9i, b\u1ea1n kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 t\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ed9ng b\u00e1n h\u00e0ng m\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u00f3ng vai tr\u00f2 trung gian t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u00e1c v\u00e0 qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o ti\u1ebfp th\u1ecb cho website.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>D\u1ec5 nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5y nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 c\u00e1c trang web th\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1ea1i \u0111i\u1ec7n t\u1eed, ng\u01b0\u1eddi mua \u0111\u1ebfn website v\u00e0 ch\u1ecdn t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m c\u1ea7n mua, sau \u0111\u00f3 ti\u1ebfn h\u00e0nh thanh to\u00e1n online. T\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 di\u1ec5n ra t\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ed9ng v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i ng\u0169 x\u1eed l\u00fd \u0111\u01a1n h\u00e0ng s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfn h\u00e0nh giao h\u00e0ng cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi mua.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"alignleft\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1024\" height=\"559\" src=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/Check-Out-Page-1024x559.png\" alt=\"Check Out Page\" class=\"wp-image-17156\" srcset=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/Check-Out-Page-1024x559.png 1024w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/Check-Out-Page-218x119.png 218w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/Check-Out-Page-300x164.png 300w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/Check-Out-Page-700x382.png 700w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/Check-Out-Page-768x419.png 768w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/Check-Out-Page.png 1242w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><figcaption>Kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng thanh to\u00e1n t\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ed9ng<\/figcaption><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p>B\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 b\u00e1n h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 c\u00f4ng b\u1eb1ng Facebook Fanpage. B\u1ea1n nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01a1n h\u00e0ng t\u1eeb Messenger sau \u0111\u00f3 x\u1eed l\u00fd \u0111\u01a1n h\u00e0ng t\u1eeb th\u00f4ng tin ng\u01b0\u1eddi mua cung c\u1ea5p. Quy tr\u00ecnh n\u00e0y c\u1ea7n b\u1ea1n s\u00e1t sao v\u1edbi doanh nghi\u1ec7p, v\u00e0 k\u00e9m chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>\u0110\u1ec3 ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n, b\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng t\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ed9ng h\u01a1n l\u00e0 th\u1ee7 c\u00f4ng, b\u1ea1n ph\u1ea3i x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng t\u1ef1 ch\u1ea1y ngay c\u1ea3 khi kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 b\u1ea1n. Facebook Fanpage ch\u1ec9 n\u00ean \u0111\u00f3ng vai tr\u00f2 t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u00e1c v\u00e0 cung c\u1ea5p th\u00f4ng tin cho kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1024\" height=\"695\" src=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/Facebook-Messenger-tuong-tac-1024x695.png\" alt=\"Facebook Messenger Tuong Tac\" class=\"wp-image-17161\" srcset=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/Facebook-Messenger-tuong-tac-1024x695.png 1024w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/Facebook-Messenger-tuong-tac-218x148.png 218w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/Facebook-Messenger-tuong-tac-300x204.png 300w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/Facebook-Messenger-tuong-tac-700x475.png 700w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/Facebook-Messenger-tuong-tac-768x521.png 768w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/Facebook-Messenger-tuong-tac.png 1600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><figcaption>Facebook Messenger (Facebook Fanpage) n\u00ean gi\u1eef vai tr\u00f2 \u0111i\u1ec1u h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi website<\/figcaption><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p>X\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng website l\u00e0 x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng ch\u1ea1y t\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ed9ng, chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ed5i t\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ed9ng, ch\u0103m s\u00f3c t\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ed9ng, b\u00e1n h\u00e0ng t\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ed9ng v\u00e0 v\u1eadn chuy\u1ec3n s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m t\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ed9ng. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau b\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi khi m\u1edf r\u1ed9ng doanh nghi\u1ec7p trong th\u1eddi gian d\u00e0i.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2>3. Thu th\u1eadp th\u00f4ng tin kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng t\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ed9ng (h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 ch\u1ea1y qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o Facebook Ads)<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Hi\u1ec7n nay ch\u1ea1y qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o Facebook \u0111em l\u1ea1i k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t cho doanh s\u1ed1 b\u00e1n h\u00e0ng, tuy nhi\u00ean n\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 website l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 l\u00e3ng ph\u00ed r\u1ea5t gh\u00ea g\u1edbm.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Khi kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ebfn website b\u1ea1n, ngo\u00e0i chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ed5i b\u00e1n h\u00e0nh, thu th\u1eadp th\u00f4ng tin v\u00e0 email c\u1ee7a kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng cho chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o k\u1ebf ti\u1ebfp l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ed1t l\u00f5i c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 marketing trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai nh\u01b0 follow, pre-sale, feedback,&#8230;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1024\" height=\"752\" src=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/Social-Media-Manager-Opt-In-Page-1024x752.png\" alt=\"Social Media Manager Opt In Page\" class=\"wp-image-17151\" srcset=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/Social-Media-Manager-Opt-In-Page-1024x752.png 1024w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/Social-Media-Manager-Opt-In-Page-218x160.png 218w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/Social-Media-Manager-Opt-In-Page-300x220.png 300w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/Social-Media-Manager-Opt-In-Page-700x514.png 700w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/Social-Media-Manager-Opt-In-Page-768x564.png 768w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/Social-Media-Manager-Opt-In-Page.png 1246w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><figcaption>D\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf trang thu th\u1eadp email kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng cho marketing sau n\u00e0y v\u1edbi Website<\/figcaption><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p>C\u00e1c h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng c\u1eeda h\u00e0ng b\u00e1n l\u1ebb c\u0169ng \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt n\u00e0y, sau khi b\u1ea1n mua h\u00e0ng, nh\u00e2n vi\u00ean s\u1ebd y\u00eau c\u1ea7u email c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ec3 l\u01b0u v\u00e0o h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng ch\u0103m s\u00f3c kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>V\u00ec h\u1ecd bi\u1ebft r\u1eb1ng ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 t\u1ed1t kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng c\u0169 s\u1ebd gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ed5i g\u1ea5p 6 l\u1ea7n so v\u1edbi kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng m\u1edbi.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Website c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n c\u0169ng c\u00f3 ch\u1ee9c n\u0103ng t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f2n t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n v\u00ec ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thi\u1ebft l\u1eadp thu th\u1eadp t\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ed9ng.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Sau khi b\u1ea1n ch\u1ea1y qu\u1ea3ng c\u00e1o Facebook, b\u1ea1n \u0111i\u1ec1u h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ebfn website c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ed5i th\u00e0nh doanh s\u1ed1 b\u00e1n h\u00e0ng v\u1edbi copywriting. Kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng s\u1ebd t\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ed9ng mua h\u00e0nh v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i th\u00f4ng tin.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Ch\u1ec9 khi b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 website th\u00ec t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra t\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ed9ng, c\u00e1i m\u00e0 m\u1ea1ng x\u00e3 h\u1ed9i s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2>4. T\u0103ng tr\u01b0\u1edfng t\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ed9ng theo th\u1eddi gian<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1024\" height=\"622\" src=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/Google-Analytics-grow-up-1024x622.png\" alt=\"Google Analytics Grow Up\" class=\"wp-image-17166\" srcset=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/Google-Analytics-grow-up-1024x622.png 1024w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/Google-Analytics-grow-up-218x132.png 218w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/Google-Analytics-grow-up-300x182.png 300w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/Google-Analytics-grow-up-700x425.png 700w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/Google-Analytics-grow-up-768x466.png 768w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/Google-Analytics-grow-up.png 1176w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><figcaption>B\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n doanh nghi\u1ec7p t\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ed9ng theo th\u1eddi gian<\/figcaption><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p>V\u1edbi SEO organic website c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd d\u1ea7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c x\u1ebfp h\u1ea1ng cao h\u01a1n theo th\u1eddi gian v\u00e0 n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n. Khi \u0111\u00f3 b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd d\u1ea7n kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i ti\u1ebfp th\u1ecb tr\u1ea3 ph\u00ed n\u1eefa.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>M\u1ed7i ng\u00e0y kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1m n\u0103ng s\u1ebd t\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u00ecm \u0111\u1ebfn website c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n v\u00e0 chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ed5i t\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ed9ng. Khi \u0111\u00f3 b\u1ea1n ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n ch\u1ea1y qu\u1ea3